title: TITANIC Shipwreck Exploration-SKIDROW
description:
TITANIC Shipwreck Exploration-SKIDROW 

Titanic Shipwreck Exploration is a diving simulator and immersive
interactive story, with over 6 hours of game-play. It you will leave
with a greater understanding of the historic tragedy that unfolded in
1912 leading to the sinking of the worlds most famous ship

NOTE: This version of the game is a desktop optimized version of
Titanic VR. This title is designed to be played on a standard
monitor with either a keyboard and mouse our an X Box controller

INSTALL NOTES

1. Unpack the release
2. Mount or burn image
3. Install
4. Block the game in your firewall and mark our cracked content as
secure/trusted in your antivirus program
